Package de.db.derPate.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    This dataclass is used to store Admins login credentials and to make the Admin recognized as such, as the LoginUser stored in the user's HttpSession (see LoginManager) can be typecasted back.
    Godfather
    This dataclass is used for the godfather login and profile edit and for displaying all godfathers, when logged in as a trainee.
    GodfatherInformation
    This dataclass is used to hold all informations used for displaying a list of Godfathers to the trainee.
    LoginUser
    Baseclass of all classes, that can store data, which you can use to log on.
    Trainee
    Class that holds all the informations of an trainee.
    UsernamePasswordLogin
    Abstract class that is used by all classes, that are using email and password as login credentials.
